  ('16860df1-6e4a-5283-9296-6042bd5b69f2', 'TAT_RF_0101', 'IND_TAT_D01', 'ROLE0101_DR01', 'Ring Spinning Supervisor operates in Yarn Spinning Batch and Machine Process Control within Fibre, Yarn and Spinning Manufacturing of Textiles, Apparel & Technical Textiles. The workplace setting is Mill spinning floor covering bale mixing, fibre opening, carding, drawing, roving, spinning, winding, yarn testing, and dispatch handoff.. The role handles Bale mix, card sliver, roving, yarn lot, machine setting, winding record using ERP/MIS, spinning frame records, Uster/yarn testing instruments, winding reports, production logbooks. Day to day, it reviews role-specific inputs, performs the assigned production, testing, coordination or evidence action, records exceptions, updates controlled records and prepares handoff evidence. Its authority level is Recommend; decisions outside this boundary, including final release, certification, approval or exception override, must be escalated to the authorised owner. Output proof includes Bale mix sheet, machine setting sheet, shift output tracker, winding record.', 'E', 'C', 'R', 'ECR', 'Ring Spinning Supervisor is mapped to ECR because work in Yarn Spinning Batch and Machine Process Control requires enterprising activity as the strongest environment, supported by conventional and realistic demands. The role combines Bale mix, card sliver, roving, yarn lot, machine setting, winding record with controlled records, evidence review, task execution and authority-aware handoff.', 'Checks Bale mix, card sliver, roving, yarn lot, machine setting, winding record against the current requirement; uses ERP/MIS, spinning frame records, Uster/yarn testing instruments, winding reports, production logbooks; identifies missing, mismatched or out-of-tolerance evidence; records the finding; completes or updates Bale mix sheet, machine setting sheet, shift output tracker, winding record; selects the permitted continue, hold, retest, correct or escalate acti